BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//Daksh Avtani//Fitness Journey PPL Split//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Push Pull Legs Split - Daksh Avtani
X-WR-CALDESC:6-day Push/Pull/Legs training split (Mon-Sat) with exercises.
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ppl-overview-2026@daksh-fitness-journey
DTSTAMP:20260611T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260621
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260622
SUMMARY:Push / Pull / Legs split overview
DESCRIPTION:6-day Push\, Pull\, Legs split. Train Monday to Saturday\, rest Sunday. Runs 21 June to 28 December.\n\nWEEK STRUCTURE\nMon: Push 1\nTue: Pull 1\nWed: Legs 1\nThu: Push 2\nFri: Pull 2\nSat: Legs 2\nSun: Rest\n\nPUSH 1 (chest, shoulders, triceps)\n1. Incline smith machine press\n2. Dumbbell bench press\n3. Pec deck fly\n4. Shoulder press\n5. Straight bar tricep pushdown\n6. Cable lateral raise or lateral raise machine\n7. Skull crushers\n\nPULL 1 (back, biceps, traps, abs)\n1. Preacher curls\n2. Wide-grip lat pulldown\n3. T-bar rows\n4. Incline dumbbell curls\n5. Shrugs\n6. Abs superset: leg raises, cable crunches, hip raises\n\nLEGS 1 (quads, hamstrings, calves)\n1. Leg press or squats\n2. Leg extension\n3. Hamstring curls\n4. Standing calf raises (incl. smith machine option)\n5. Romanian deadlifts\n\nPUSH 2 (chest, shoulders, triceps - variation)\n1. Dumbbell bench press\n2. Incline smith machine press\n3. Decline bench press\n4. Shoulder press\n5. Straight bar tricep pushdown\n6. Cable lateral raise\n7. Skull crushers\n\nPULL 2 (back, biceps, rear delts)\n1. Preacher curls\n2. Wide-grip lat pulldown\n3. Seated cable rows\n4. Cable curls\n5. Rear delts on pec deck fly\n6. Hammer curls\n\nLEGS 2 (optional second leg day)\n1. Leg press or squats\n2. Leg extension\n3. Hamstring curls\n4. Standing calf raises\n5. Romanian deadlifts
END:VEVENT
